      "description": "$29,900 - Clean, good-looking car that\u2019s been kept up well and offers a really nice balance of condition, enjoyment, and value. It presents well overall, has the kind of honest, cared-for feel buyers appreciate, and should make someone a very satisfying driver or weekend car without stepping into top-of-market pricing. Not a perfect showpiece, but a solid, attractive example with plenty to like.",
