    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Runs and moves, but this is a poor-condition vehicle being sold honestly as a cheap project or basic transportation. It shows heavy wear inside and out, with noticeable cosmetic issues, and buyers should expect mechanical needs, deferred maintenance, and repairs. Interior and exterior both show age and use, and it does not present like a clean daily driver. Best suited for someone handy, a parts buyer, or anyone looking for an inexpensive vehicle and willing to put work into it.",
