    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers practical value for the right buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone looking for affordable transportation, a starter car, or a hands-on project with potential. Priced to reflect condition while still presenting a solid opportunity to own at a very accessible entry point.",
