    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner that could make a great cheap commuter, first project, or spare set of wheels. It shows its age and has its share of wear, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want something affordable and straightforward without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit. Come have a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running engine, responsive transmission, and good bones for someone who knows their way around a wrench. It shows wear and needs cosmetic/mechanical sorting, but the core drivetrain feels capable and the chassis is a great starting point for a budget build, daily fixer, or weekend project. Honest used car with plenty of upside for the right buyer\u2014priced to move and worth a look if you want something affordable with real potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
